Class JavaProcessMonitor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.management.DynamicMBean, javax.management.MBeanRegistration, javax.management.NotificationBroadcaster, javax.management.NotificationEmitter, BaseObjectNamed, JavaProcessMonitorMBean, SelfEmailingMBean

    public abstract class JavaProcessMonitor
extends SelfAwareMBean
implements JavaProcessMonitorMBean, javax.management.NotificationEmitter
    Abstract implementation of JavaProcessMonitorMBean that implements everything necessary to instantiate this MBean except getObjectNameSuffix(). This implementation does not place any trust restrictions upon registerProcess() callers, leaving that up to sub-classes' disgression.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
